column8: A relation between a data content and its basic building blocks or components
A relation between a data content and its distinctive qualitative or quantitative characteristics
A relation between a data content and its measurement units for quantitative data
Indicates interdependencies between data content
Specifies dependency on a data content
Establishes the access restrictions to indicate permissions and limitations on who can access the data
Establishes a relation to outline the legal and contractual obligations associated with the data
A relation between a dataset and its quality check or control pass
Establishes a relation between a dataset and its usage guidelines, providing recommendations and best practices for utilizing the data
A relation that specifies Digital Object Identifier (DOI) of a published entity to make it publicly available
specifies the contact information of an authority to discuss about the dataset as a usage guideline
Specifies the date of copyright information at which the dataset to indicate ownership and intellectual property rights
Specifies the identified name of a Data content for popular referencing and identification
Specifies a comprehensive description of a Data content
Specifies a person or organisation that provides the dataset
Specifies objectives or goals associated with the dataset
Provides a textual description of the dataset
Describes the purpose or intended use of the dataset
Specifies a date when the dataset was originally created
Specifies the size of the dataset
Specifies the maximum value
Specifies the minimum value
Specifies how the dataset should be cited
Specifies the contact details for individuals or entities responsible for inquiries or further information related to the dataset usage
